{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01QAkYosx9UUXK8tWHeUZ3wH","type":"tool_result","content":"package com.coffeeshop.orders.domain;\n\nimport jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\nimport jakarta.inject.Inject;\nimport jakarta.persistence.EntityManager;\nimport jakarta.transaction.Transactional;\n\n@ApplicationScoped\npublic class OrderRepository {\n\n    @Inject\n    EntityManager em;\n\n    @Transactional\n    public Long save(OrderEntity e) {\n        em.persist(e);\n        em.flush();\n        return e.getId();\n    }\n\n    public OrderEntity find(long id) {\n        return em.find(OrderEntity.class, id);\n    }\n}","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01PWWVruPQyuEii8v56MeqDs","session_id":"09dd8e6e-4ff1-445a-9c42-b2dfa0ace457","uuid":"a2963076-e2f7-4186-89db-7af5c77dcee5"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_016djToxTFLftHSzpA6m313Y","type":"tool_result","content":"package com.coffeeshop.orders.messaging;\n\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.core.JsonProcessingException;\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper;\nimport jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\nimport jakarta.inject.Inject;\nimport org.eclipse.microprofile.reactive.messaging.Channel;\nimport org.eclipse.microprofile.reactive.messaging.Emitter;\n\n@ApplicationScoped\npublic class OrdersPipeline {\n\n    @Inject\n    @Channel(\"barista\")\n    Emitter<String> barista;\n\n    @Inject\n    @Channel(\"kitchen\")\n    Emitter<String> kitchen;\n\n    private static final ObjectMapper MAPPER = new ObjectMapper();\n\n    public void publishToBarista(OrderCommand cmd) {\n        try {\n            System.out.println(\"[orders] sending barista command: \" + cmd);","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01PWWVruPQyuEii8v56MeqDs","session_id":"09dd8e6e-4ff1-445a-9c42-b2dfa0ace457","uuid":"d9c8cab8-0435-4f86-a09a-2890e06809b6"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01PWWVruPQyuEii8v56MeqDs","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Summary\n\nI have successfully refactored the Jakarta EE / Open Liberty coffee shop application to Quarkus. Here's what was done:\n\n### Files Deleted (JAX-RS Application classes not needed in Quarkus):\n1. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/orders-service/src/main/java/com/coffeeshop/orders/api/OrdersApplication.java**\n2. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/orders-service/src/main/java/com/coffeeshop/orders/web/RestApp.java**\n3. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/orders-service/src/main/java/com/coffeeshop/orders/api/OrdersResource.java** (duplicate)\n4. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/barista-service/src/main/java/com/coffeeshop/barista/api/BaristaApplication.java**\n5. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/kitchen-service/src/main/java/com/coffeeshop/kitchen/api/KitchenApplication.java**\n\n### Files Refactored for Quarkus:\n\n#### orders-service module:\n1. **OrdersResource.java** - Added OrderRepository injection and implemented proper GET method to retrieve OrderEntity with 404 handling\n2. **OrderRepository.java** - Changed from `@PersistenceContext(unitName = \"ordersPU\")` to `@Inject EntityManager`, added `em.flush()` in save method\n3. **OrderService.java** - Added `@Transactional` annotation to the `place()` method\n4. **OrdersPipeline.java** - Replaced JSON-B (`Jsonb`) with Jackson (`ObjectMapper`) for JSON serialization\n5. **OrderUpdatesListener.java** - Replaced JSON-B with Jackson for JSON deserialization\n\n#### barista-service module:\n6. **BaristaConsumer.java** - Replaced JSON-B with Jackson for JSON processing\n\n#### kitchen-service module:\n7. **KitchenConsumer.java** - Replaced javax.json with Jackson for JSON processing\n\n### Files Kept As-Is (compatible with Quarkus):\n- All files in **common** module (OrderRequest.java, OrderAck.java, OrderStatus.java)\n- **OrderEntity.java** (Jakarta Persistence annotations work in Quarkus)\n- **BasicHealth.java** in all services (MicroProfile Health is supported)\n- **StatusResource.java** in barista and kitchen services\n- **ConstraintViolationExceptionMapper.java** in orders-service\n\n### Key Changes Made:\n1. **Persistence**: Changed from `@PersistenceContext` to `@Inject` for EntityManager (Quarkus style)\n2. **JSON Processing**: Replaced JSON-B and javax.json with Jackson (Quarkus default)\n3. **Transactions**: Added `@Transactional` on service methods where needed\n4. **Application Classes**: Removed JAX-RS Application classes (Quarkus auto-discovers resources)\n5. **Error Handling**: Improved GET endpoint to return 404 when entity not found\n\nAll refactored files maintain the same business logic while using Quarkus-compatible patterns and libraries."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"09dd8e6e-4ff1-445a-9c42-b2dfa0ace457","uuid":"28920e90-bab5-4f2b-b4b3-301b0b90e4fd"}
