{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01GbJemZkBbQXFvwLCRCX6Wd","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me create the Quarkus application.properties files and remove obsolete Liberty configs. For the orders-service, I need to configure:\n- H2 datasource for standalone mode  \n- Hibernate ORM  \n- Kafka reactive messaging (with graceful startup when Kafka unavailable)  \n- REST path prefix `/api`  \n- Health checks  \n\nSince the Docker container will run standalone without Kafka/PostgreSQL, I need to make Kafka messaging optional. The best approach in Quarkus is to use in-memory connectors or disable the health check for Kafka."}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":438,"cache_read_input_tokens":94861,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":438,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":995},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"09dd8e6e-4ff1-445a-9c42-b2dfa0ace457","uuid":"14f6e52d-f8ea-420f-8416-01534a440c76"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01GbJemZkBbQXFvwLCRCX6Wd","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_011AnRK3v3KLZWqMYWbqitR4","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/orders-service/src/main/resources/application.properties","content":"# =============================================\n# Quarkus Orders Service Configuration\n# =============================================\n\n# REST API base path (replaces @ApplicationPath(\"/api\"))\nquarkus.rest.path=/api\nquarkus.http.port=8080\n\n# =============================================\n# Datasource Configuration (H2 in-memory default)\n# =============================================\nquarkus.datasource.db-kind=h2\nquarkus.datasource.jdbc.url=jdbc:h2:mem:coffeeshop;DB_CLOSE_DELAY=-1\nquarkus.datasource.username=sa\nquarkus.datasource.password=\n\n# PostgreSQL configuration (activate with -Dquarkus.profile=prod)\n%prod.quarkus.datasource.db-kind=postgresql\n%prod.quarkus.datasource.jdbc.url=jdbc:postgresql://${DB_HOST:localhost}:${DB_PORT:5432}/${DB_NAME:coffeeshop}\n%prod.quarkus.datasource.username=${DB_USER:cafe}\n%prod.quarkus.datasource.password=${DB_PASSWORD:cafe}\n\n# Hibernate ORM\nquarkus.hibernate-orm.database.generation=drop-and-create\nquarkus.hibernate-orm.log.sql=false\n%prod.quarkus.hibernate-orm.database.generation=update\n\n# =============================================\n# Kafka / Reactive Messaging Configuration\n# =============================================\nkafka.bootstrap.servers=${KAFKA_BOOTSTRAP:localhost:9092}\n\n# Outgoing: barista commands\nmp.messaging.outgoing.barista.connector=smallrye-kafka\nmp.messaging.outgoing.barista.topic=barista-commands\nmp.messaging.outgoing.barista.value.serializer=org.apache.kafka.common.serialization.StringSerializer\n\n# Outgoing: kitchen commands\nmp.messaging.outgoing.kitchen.connector=smallrye-kafka\nmp.messaging.outgoing.kitchen.topic=kitchen-commands\nmp.messaging.outgoing.kitchen.value.serializer=org.apache.kafka.common.serialization.StringSerializer\n\n# Incoming: order updates\nmp.messaging.incoming.order-updates.connector=smallrye-kafka\nmp.messaging.incoming.order-updates.topic=order-updates\nmp.messaging.incoming.order-updates.value.deserializer=org.apache.kafka.common.serialization.StringDeserializer\nmp.messaging.incoming.order-updates.group.id=orders-service\nmp.messaging.incoming.order-updates.auto.offset.reset=latest\nmp.messaging.incoming.order-updates.failure-strategy=ignore\n\n# Kafka health check disabled (allows standalone startup without Kafka)\nquarkus.kafka.health.enabled=false\nquarkus.reactive-messaging.health.enabled=false\n\n# =============================================\n# Health checks\n# =============================================\nquarkus.smallrye-health.root-path=/q/health\n\n# =============================================\n# Static resources (serve from META-INF/resources)\n# =============================================\nquarkus.http.enable-compression=true\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":438,"cache_read_input_tokens":94861,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":438,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":995},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"09dd8e6e-4ff1-445a-9c42-b2dfa0ace457","uuid":"6cb2a8af-4f1f-4813-bde4-b0cc20afa50e"}
