{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01X5UNUWSz4vAALwhjsKazxg","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package com.coffeeshop.common.domain;\n     2→\n     3→import jakarta.validation.constraints.Min;\n     4→import jakarta.validation.constraints.NotBlank;\n     5→\n     6→public record OrderRequest(\n     7→    @NotBlank String customer,\n     8→    @NotBlank String item,\n     9→    @Min(1) int quantity\n    10→) {}\n    11→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"09dd8e6e-4ff1-445a-9c42-b2dfa0ace457","uuid":"cb47c1ac-9030-4d2b-83b3-88ae80cd0727"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01VJf8yhQdzGrRaDrXU2doJ9","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issue is that with Java records, the `@NotBlank` annotation on record components doesn't propagate to the correct target for Hibernate Validator in Quarkus REST. The annotation needs `@field:` or we need to convert this to a regular class, or we need to use `@Valid` with a different approach. \n\nActually, the real issue is that Quarkus REST (RESTEasy Reactive) deserializes records from JSON and then validates - but the validator sees the record *constructor parameter* type, not the field. This is a known issue. The fix is to convert OrderRequest from a record to a regular POJO with getters/setters, or use constructor-level validation properly.\n\nThe simplest fix: convert `OrderRequest` to a plain POJO class:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":407,"cache_read_input_tokens":126597,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":407,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":612},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"09dd8e6e-4ff1-445a-9c42-b2dfa0ace457","uuid":"f228c312-7cc5-49c0-9a00-70817e0e914b"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01VJf8yhQdzGrRaDrXU2doJ9","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01VmDqYSauyLtC4H5eNcARQ3","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/common/src/main/java/com/coffeeshop/common/domain/OrderRequest.java","content":"package com.coffeeshop.common.domain;\n\nimport jakarta.validation.constraints.Min;\nimport jakarta.validation.constraints.NotBlank;\n\npublic class OrderRequest {\n\n    @NotBlank\n    private String customer;\n\n    @NotBlank\n    private String item;\n\n    @Min(1)\n    private int quantity;\n\n    public OrderRequest() {\n    }\n\n    public OrderRequest(String customer, String item, int quantity) {\n        this.customer = customer;\n        this.item = item;\n        this.quantity = quantity;\n    }\n\n    public String customer() {\n        return customer;\n    }\n\n    public String item() {\n        return item;\n    }\n\n    public int quantity() {\n        return quantity;\n    }\n\n    public String getCustomer() {\n        return customer;\n    }\n\n    public void setCustomer(String customer) {\n        this.customer = customer;\n    }\n\n    public String getItem() {\n        return item;\n    }\n\n    public void setItem(String item) {\n        this.item = item;\n    }\n\n    public int getQuantity() {\n        return quantity;\n    }\n\n    public void setQuantity(int quantity) {\n        this.quantity = quantity;\n    }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":407,"cache_read_input_tokens":126597,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":407,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":612},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"09dd8e6e-4ff1-445a-9c42-b2dfa0ace457","uuid":"5c53a88c-00ef-4230-aa49-a