{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01WwMWko1agKtVeWtKe2AX8K","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks complete. Here's the final summary:\n\n## Migration Complete: Jakarta EE (Open Liberty) -> Quarkus 3.17.8\n\n### Results\n- **Smoke Tests**: 7/7 passing\n- **Docker Image**: Builds and runs successfully\n- **All Endpoints Working**:\n  - `GET /q/health/ready` -> 200 UP\n  - `GET /q/health/live` -> 200 UP\n  - `POST /api/orders` (valid) -> 202 with `{\"id\":\"...\"}` \n  - `POST /api/orders` (invalid) -> 400 with validation errors\n  - `GET /api/orders/{id}` -> 200 with order data\n  - `GET /api/orders/999` -> 404\n\n### Key Changes Made\n1. **Build**: Replaced Liberty plugin + WAR packaging with Quarkus plugin + uber-jar\n2. **Dependencies**: Jakarta EE / MicroProfile -> Quarkus extensions (REST, Hibernate ORM, H2, Kafka, Health, Validator)\n3. **Configuration**: Liberty `server.xml` -> Quarkus `application.properties`\n4. **Serialization**: JSON-B/JSON-P -> Jackson\n5. **JPA**: `@PersistenceContext` -> `@Inject EntityManager`\n6. **Validation**: Java record -> POJO with field-level annotations + manual `Validator.validate()` \n7. **Transaction Safety**: Separated DB persistence from Kafka messaging to avoid `RollbackException` when Kafka is unavailable\n8. **Jandex**: Added `jandex-maven-plugin` to common module for build-time annotation discovery\n\n### Documentation\nFull details in `CHANGELOG.md`."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":750,"cache_read_input_tokens":55551,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":750,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":414},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"09dd8e6e-4ff1-445a-9c42-b2dfa0ace457","uuid":"aa58a92c-c542-4144-803e-a6d27e1f60f3"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":3315007,"duration_api_ms":1838798,"num_turns":208,"result":"All tasks complete. Here's the final summary:\n\n## Migration Complete: Jakarta EE (Open Liberty) -> Quarkus 3.17.8\n\n### Results\n- **Smoke Tests**: 7/7 passing\n- **Docker Image**: Builds and runs successfully\n- **All Endpoints Working**:\n  - `GET /q/health/ready` -> 200 UP\n  - `GET /q/health/live` -> 200 UP\n  - `POST /api/orders` (valid) -> 202 with `{\"id\":\"...\"}` \n  - `POST /api/orders` (invalid) -> 400 with validation errors\n  - `GET /api/orders/{id}` -> 200 with order data\n  - `GET /api/orders/999` -> 404\n\n### Key Changes Made\n1. **Build**: Replaced Liberty plugin + WAR packaging with Quarkus plugin + uber-jar\n2. **Dependencies**: Jakarta EE / MicroProfile -> Quarkus extensions (REST, Hibernate ORM, H2, Kafka, Health, Validator)\n3. **Configuration**: Liberty `server.xml` -> Quarkus `application.properties`\n4. **Serialization**: JSON-B/JSON-P -> Jackson\n5. **JPA**: `@PersistenceContext` -> `@Inject EntityManager`\n6. **Validation**: Java record -> POJO with field-level annotations + manual `Validator.validate()` \n7. **Transaction Safety**: Separated DB persistence from Kafka messaging to avoid `RollbackException` when Kafka is unavailable\n8. **Jandex**: Added `jandex-maven-plugin` to common module for build-time annotation discovery\n\n### Documentation\nFull details in `CHANGELOG.md`.","session_id":"09dd8e6e-4ff1-445a-9c42-b2dfa0ace457","total_cost_usd":33.989533749999964,"usage":{"input_tokens":142,"cache_creation_input_tokens":322223,"cache_read_input_tokens":13169800,"output_tokens":58731,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":322223}},"modelUsage":{"aws/claude-3-5-haiku":{"inputTokens":270121,"outputTokens":8880,"cacheReadInputTokens":119455,"cacheCreationInputTokens":10716,"webSear